"{\"uid\": \"bordermail.com.au-story-8685822-man-critical-after-two-truck-crash-on-olympic-highway-near-the-rock\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited content and the digital versions of our print editions - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A man has been left fighting for his life and another seriously injuredafter a two-truck crash on Wednesday afternoon.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  Emergency services including two rescue helicopters were called to the Olympic Highway just north of The Rock, on Wednesday, July 3, about 1.15pm after two trucks collided head-on.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The highway was shut in both directions and a major emergency operation unfolded at the scene with the driver of a garbage truck and the driver of a truck and dog both trapped in the wreck.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Investigators worked through the night at the scene, with Riverina Police District's Inspector Lee Gray on Thursday, July 4, urging witnesses or anyone information or dashcam footage to contact the Wagga station or Crime Stoppers.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3725243397908968e-14, \"text\": \"Riverina\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riverina\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"score\": 0.9999698898772561, \"rank\": 2.866488072093535e-05, \"text\": \"Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Edward_Gray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NSW Ambulance Riverina Inspector Eamonn Purcell said the 54-year-old man who had been driving the garbage truck was in a \\\"very critical\\\" condition at the time he was flown to Canberra Hospital.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\", \"score\": 0.9916826278818105, \"rank\": 0.008387120329391222, \"text\": \"Purcell\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\", \"score\": 0.999999434804227, \"rank\": 5.651959639069707e-07, \"text\": \"Canberra Hospital\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had injuries to his chest and lower limbs, Inspector Purcell said.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\", \"score\": 0.9916826278818105, \"rank\": 0.008387120329391222, \"text\": \"Purcell\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Purcell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 50-year-old, who had been driving the truck and dog combination, was also in a \\\"very serious\\\" condition and taken to Canberra Hospital.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\", \"score\": 0.999999434804227, \"rank\": 5.651959639069707e-07, \"text\": \"Canberra Hospital\", \"types\": 